node.text: In honor of LGBTQ+ #Pride month, we spoke to “Zoey’s Extraordinary Playlist” star @thealexnewell about the importance of queer representation in media. ❤️

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 3 people.

node.text: And then there were 4! Shawn Johnson and  Andrew East welcomed their second child together, a baby boy! 💙 Link in bio for all the details on their bundle of joy. (📷: Instagram)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, child and indoor.

node.text: Mariah Carey and Nick Cannon's daughter Monroe just made her modeling debut. ❤️ Click the link in our bio to see her first campaign. (📷: Getty)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, suit and text that says '"LOVE IS NEVER MORE RELEVANT THAN IT IS RIGHT NOW." -JENNIFER LOPEZ E'.

node.text: Her love don't cost a thing, but Jennifer Lopez isn't quick to respond to questions about her romance with Ben Affleck.  Link in bio for her reaction to a question about her relationship. (📷: Getty)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on July 20, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, indoor and text that says 'BU'.

node.text: Adele's new romance has us rolling in the deep. 😍 Say hello to the link in our bio for everything we know about her new beau. ❤️(📷: Getty)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on July 19, 2021. May be a black-and-white image of 2 people.

node.text: @ Lola we need your reaction because your parents just posted their cheekiest photo yet. Link in bio for Mark Consuelos & Kelly Ripa's 🔥🍑 moment. (📷: Instagram)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by E! News on July 19, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, standing and indoor.

node.text: If you hear something, that's the sound of us crying into our rosé after tonight's #Bachelorette. Link in bio for Katie's heart-wrenching goodbye to a fan favorite. 💔 (📷: ABC)

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by E! News on July 19, 2021 tagging @sarahjessicaparker. May be an image of 1 person, standing and outdoors.

node.text: And just like that, we got carried away. 👑(📷: Getty)
